<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gepette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, ewch wissen ze <expan>lass<ex>en,</ex></expan> ob uns von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan>, den von Ulme, iht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan> wer als von des diensts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und laszen ewr
                                <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns noch niht treffenlichs von den von
                        Ulme <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan> ist, denn sie
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns nehst
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, daz sie und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gut <expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>swebisch<ex>en</ex></expan> stett, die mit in in
                                <expan>eynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> sint, eins
                            <expan>gemeine<ex>n</ex></expan> diensts <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>r<ex>ömischen</ex></expan>
<expan>k<ex>ünig</ex></expan>, ze tun noch niht
                            <expan>ub<ex>er</ex>ein</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Doch so <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sie von <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> ze<expan>same<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein. Wie es sich da bey in gemacht hab
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> machen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>,
                                <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> wir noch niht. Und wer, daz uns von
                        den von Ulme furbas iht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan>
<add>wurde</add>, daz uns treffenlich <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>notdurft<ex>en</ex></expan> dewht, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> ze
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künd<ex>en,</ex></expan> das
                            <expan>wolt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun.
                        Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
